Marinated Steak
---------------
A zesty marinated steak, perfect for a main course.

Ingredients
---------------
1 Steak, of any type
3 Ounces of whiskey
1 Orange

Directions
--------------- 
Put the steak and whiskey into a pot.  Juice the orange and put the
juice into the pot.  Chop up the remaining orange place in pot.  Cook
steak until done and remove orange pieces before serving.

